奥斯卡（Oscar）获得格莱美奖（Grammy）获奖者，提名尼日利亚歌手兼作词人<a href="https://twitter.com/temsbaby?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Temsbaby</a>加入了圣地亚哥足球俱乐部所有权集团，成为俱乐部合作伙伴。</p><p> TEMS成为第一个参与MLS所有权的非洲女性。</p><p>读<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2935.png" alt="⤵" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> - 圣地亚哥足球俱乐部（@sandiegofc） <a href="https://twitter.com/sandiegofc/status/1889706165912871274?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月12日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p></p><p> Other investors alongside Tems include actress and producer Issa Rae, former Spanish footballer Juan Mata, retired US Navy SEAL Jocko Willink, and Major League Baseball star Manny Machado.</p><p> Tems has also shared how she is committed to developing young football talents through partnering with Right to Dream Academy, an initiative that works with young people to develop and mentor future football stars.</p><p>她补充说：“音乐和体育在为年轻才华和下一代打开大门的方式上相似。” “This is why I&#39;m proud to be part of this project, especially with Right to Dream Academy, in helping to grow and develop future stars,” she further explained.</p><p> Right to Dream is described in a press release as a “global football community of world-class academies, clubs and educational partners” that “provides professional football and education pathways for students.”</p><p> San Diego FC CEO Tom Penn said of the move: “Tems is an extraordinary artist and cultural force worldwide. We are honoured to have her join our Club and bring her visionary perspective to San Diego FC. </p><figure id="attachment_3837841" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837841" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837841" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC.jpg" alt="tems" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tems-San-Diego-FC-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837841" class="wp-caption-text"> TEMS现在是圣地亚哥足球俱乐部的所有者 - 信贷：新闻</figcaption></figure><p>“她对赋予下一代的热情完全符合我们的使命，而她致力于为年轻人的国内和全球创造机会，这反映了梦想权的核心价值观。我们还期待在音乐界与圣地亚哥足球俱乐部之间建立有意义的联系，并通过文化和体育的共同力量团结社区。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tems-born-in-the-wild-debut-album-tracklist-review-radar-3763453"><i>NME</i>在去年对Tems首张专辑的五星级评论中说</a>：“虽然以R＆B和Afrobeat闻名，但在这里，Tems显示出融合了对比鲜明的声音和节奏的能力，使它们可以流动和互锁 - 无缝地回荡了自由的概念。</p><p> Tems用“您的脸”和“握住”（一二拳）结束了记录。 The former assumes a jazzy, melancholic tone, with Spanish guitar licks and bold affirmations of faith. The latter, meanwhile, is a spacey love letter to growth, reminding listeners of the trial by fire one can undergo in order to achieve personal evolution.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tems-joins-san-diego-fc-as-club-partner-3837835">Tems邮政加入圣地亚哥足球俱乐部，担任俱乐部合作伙伴，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
